data.description: Welcome home! This charming 3-bedroom, 1.5-bathroom ranch is ideally situated less than 2 miles south of the Historic Medina Square. This home is a true gem, featuring a brand-new roof installed in 2023 for worry-free living. Step inside to discover a beautifully upgraded interior, highlighted by a granite kitchen with a stylish subway-tiled backsplash, added in 2015. The kitchen comes complete with stainless steel appliances and newly refaced cabinets. The spacious great room is the heart of the home, boasting a cozy wood-burning fireplace and elegant laminate flooring throughout. Enjoy the seamless flow of the floor plan, with newer windows installed in 2013 providing an abundance of natural light. The full-fenced backyard, added in 2013, offers a private oasis for outdoor gatherings and relaxation. With a perfect blend of modern updates and classic charm, this residence is ready to welcome its new owners. Don't miss the opportunity to make this house your home—call today to schedule a private showing and explore all that this property has to offer!
